text:
Newly open Japanese restaurant, cozy nice ambience.
Food is a nice, price is affordable, received a Recycle Bag will love to visit again.
Thai restaurants and Asian businesses. There is a hair wig place here, Money Changer place, clothing shops.

Nice place for great Thai food!
Toilets are so clean & there are so many cubicles even when I am nearby somewhere will head over here to use them ðŸ¤­
Directly connected to Nicoll MRT, & so accessible to so many interesting places in town, great place to live & work too.
Hope the food court opens soon yah ðŸ«¤

The shopping mall is clean and spacious, but it lacks high-traffic stores that would attract more visitors. There are nice dessert store and cosy bakery cafe at the quiet basement level, is a pleasant place to sit and enjoy food or drinks.

NO BIDET IN TOILET

I can see very elegant toilets on some floors, must have spent a fortune on them.

But there is ZERO bidet sprayer. No bidet sprayer at all.

I had to flush 10 times to use the "mini fountain" created by the flushes to clean my butthole. Must have used at least 5 liter or water there.
Saved cost by removing them? Think again
